extends layout

block content
  h1 DM Panel: Setting the mood
  p A free and open source DM panel that plays music to support your RPGs
  
  p The DM panel is in production and looking for your feedback: what feature do you really want?
  
  br
  
  p 
  b Music: Select the mood that best fits the current events in your scenario to hear appropriate music
  br
  p "Sustained music" is more appropriate to play at length
  br
 
  div(id="button-container")
  
  button(type="button", value="music1") Stop current music
  
  br
  br
  
  p Session Notes
  textarea(type="textarea",name="sessionnotes",label="Session Notes1",columns="20")
  br
  br
  br
  br
  
  b Simple NPC creator
  br
  i Design simple NPCs on the fly as you go
  br
  p 
  i Level
    br
    select(id="level")
     option(value=1) 1
     option(value=2) 2
     option(value=3) 3
     option(value=4) 4
     option(value=5) 5
     option(value=6) 6
     option(value=7) 7
     option(value=8) 8
     option(value=9) 9
     option(value=10) 10
     option(value=11) 11
     option(value=12) 12
     option(value=13) 13
     option(value=14) 14
     option(value=15) 15
     option(value=16) 16
     option(value=17) 17
     option(value=18) 18
     option(value=19) 19
     option(value=20) 20
  
  p
  i  Class
  br
  select(id="charclass")
     option(value=Barbarian) Barbarian
     option(value=Bard) Bard
     option(value=Cleric) Cleric
     option(value=Druid) Druid
     option(value=Fighter) Fighter
     option(value=Monk) Monk
     option(value=Paladin) Paladin
     option(value=Ranger) Ranger
     option(value=Rogue) Rogue
     option(value=Sorcerer) Sorcerer
     option(value=Wizard) Wizard
 
  p 
  i Name
  br
  input(type="text",id="charname")
  p
  i  Equipment Quality
  br
  select(id="equipment")
     option(value="Good") Good
     option(value="Bad") Bad
  br
  br
  br
  button(id="makechar",onclick="makecharacter()") Create character
  
  div(id="charactertext")
  
  br
  br
  br
  
  
  
  p 
  i Metaphorical tip jar (let me know how I can improve this or if there are songs you prefer for certain moods)  
  br
  p 
  i Send me an email at mfnox158@gmail.com
  
  